      "parameters": {
        "toolDescription": "Look up the EXACT relationships of one named entity (a person, team, product, or concept) directly from the knowledge graph. Returns what it connects to and how - e.g. reports to, led by, managed by, owns, uses, escalated to, routed to. Use this for any question about org structure, reporting lines, who manages or handles something, ownership, or which tools a team uses - and especially for multi-step relationship questions, looking up one entity at a time and following the chain.",
